      <title>监督机构称加拿大必须加倍国防开支才能达到北约目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/canada-must-double-annual-defense-spending-to-meet-nato-target-watchdog-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大预算监督机构表示，加拿大必须将国防开支增加近一倍，才能兑现到 2032 年达到北约提出的国防开支占国内生产总值 2% 的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/canada-must-double-annual-defense-spending-to-meet-nato-target-watchdog-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 15:05:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>外交争端升级 加拿大预测印度将发起黑客攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/canada-predicts-hacking-from-india-as-diplomatic-feud-escalates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着加拿大和印度的外交关系跌至几十年来的最低谷，加拿大正准备应对印度政府支持的黑客攻击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/canada-predicts-hacking-from-india-as-diplomatic-feud-escalates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 15:00:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国防开支推动 GDP 增长，创伊拉克战争以来最大增幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/us-defense-spending-boosts-gdp-with-biggest-surge-since-iraq-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦政府第三季度的国防支出以二十多年来最快的速度激增，帮助推动11月大选前国内生产总值上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/us-defense-spending-boosts-gdp-with-biggest-surge-since-iraq-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 14:53:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基对白宫泄露战斧导弹请求表示遗憾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/zelenskiy-laments-white-house-leak-on-tomahawk-request</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示恼怒，他向白宫提出的要求美国提供更多远程导弹的请求细节被泄露给媒体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/zelenskiy-laments-white-house-leak-on-tomahawk-request</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 14:49:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普与穆斯林的势头威胁到哈里斯在密歇根州的领先地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/trump-s-momentum-with-muslims-threatens-harris-lead-in-michigan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普担任总统期间，曾试图禁止七个穆斯林为主的国家的人进入美国。最近，他与以色列总理并肩站在一起，并使用“巴勒斯坦人”一词进行侮辱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/trump-s-momentum-with-muslims-threatens-harris-lead-in-michigan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 14:35:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登失态后，哈里斯“强烈”谴责对选民的批评</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/harris-strongly-denounces-criticism-of-voters-after-biden-flap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯表示，她“强烈”不同意总统乔·拜登的言论，共和党人认为这些言论是对唐纳德·特朗普支持者的侮辱，她试图与这场酝酿中的争议保持距离，因为这场争议可能会削弱她在竞选最后一周的势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/harris-strongly-denounces-criticism-of-voters-after-biden-flap</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 14:33:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国对俄罗斯战争机器供应商实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/us-sanctions-hundreds-of-targets-supplying-russia-s-war-machine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国正在对印度、中国和土耳其的近 400 名个人和公司实施制裁，以打击一个庞大的网络，该网络在俄罗斯全面入侵乌克兰近三年后仍帮助俄罗斯的战争机器保持运转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/us-sanctions-hundreds-of-targets-supplying-russia-s-war-machine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 14:30:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院批准弗吉尼亚州清除选举选民名册</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/supreme-court-lets-virginia-purge-voter-rolls-before-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院允许弗吉尼亚州从选民名单中清除约 1,600 名居民，并根据意识形态进行划分，这是对法官在下周总统选举中可能扮演的角色的初步考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/supreme-court-lets-virginia-purge-voter-rolls-before-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 13:57:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非预算赤字扩大 令投资者失望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/south-african-budget-debt-trajectory-worsens-growth-outlook-improves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非的预算更新显示，公共财政面临越来越大的压力，这凸显了新联合政府吸引更多投资到该地区最大经济体的必要性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/south-african-budget-debt-trajectory-worsens-growth-outlook-improves</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 12:03:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列讨论以美国为首的新协议以结束真主党冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/israel-eyes-deal-to-end-lebanon-combat-after-weakening-hezbollah</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在评估真主党武装分子的火箭弹库已基本耗尽或被摧毁后，以色列正在考虑接受由美国主导的一项协议，以结束黎巴嫩冲突并将真主党武装分子撤出以色列边境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/israel-eyes-deal-to-end-lebanon-combat-after-weakening-hezbollah</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 08:51:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
